### Create Team
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Development Team",
  "description": "Team for software development projects"
}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teams

### Get Team Details (with user role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}

### Update Team
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Development Team",
  "description": "Updated description for the development team"
}

### Get Team Participants
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}/participants

### Add Team Participant
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newmember@example.com",
  "role": 2
}

### Remove Team Participant
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}/participants/{{userId}}

### Get current user's team invitations (can be accepted)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/invitations

### Accept invitation to team as current user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}/invitations/accept

### Deny invitation to team as current user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}}/invitations/deny

### Delete Team
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/{{teamId}} 